Private Sub Display_AnimationStart()
On Error GoTo ErrHandler
'Filtrar Alarmes e Eventos por carga Dim FILTRO_CARGA As String FILTRO_CARGA = TextFiltroCarga.Caption
AlarmEventSummary1.FilterDefinition = "EventSource LIKE '%" & FILTRO_CARGA & "%'" FactoryTalkAlarmandEventLogViewer1.WhereClause = " SourceName LIKE '%" & FILTRO_CARGA & "%'"
Exit Sub
ErrHandler:
Resume Next
End Sub
